Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling on you so early.\NI'm from the state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but were you at home\Nall night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I was out drinking\Nuntil it was nearly morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital's\NDirector Heinemann;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of Surgery, Dr. Oppenheim,\Nand Dr. Boyer are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:26.08,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Murder Case\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, no one except the police\Nare allowed at the scene of the crime!\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you are obstructing\Nthe operations of the hospital.\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Press is not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,inside the hospital!\N-Please don't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to excite the patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident?\NOr was it murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people died at the same time!\NOf course it was murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything\Nabout this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!\NLet me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No one is allowed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Kenzo Tenma of this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...go right ahead.\NHey! Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NNow is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time...\N-Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma! The Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down!\NAre the emergencies taken care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, even at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been no end\Nto the emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two patients\Nwaiting to be operated on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the car accident victim\Nwith the brain contusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the X-ray Reading Room\Nto look at the x-rays first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient who collapsed due to a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor, will you help us\Nin our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that,\Nbut the initial investigation is vital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone with a grudge\Nagainst the director and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A grudge...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may consider your path\Nto becoming{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the doctor you envisioned closed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble! Those kids...\NThe twin brother and sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find them anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the sister's bed empty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked!\NBut they're nowhere to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world has happened...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...compassionately extended\Na helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely praise his lifetime\Nof achievements through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell Dr. Heinemann.\NRest in peace. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...\N-Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's difficult,\Nbut pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back my father!\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, she lived an easy life\Nas the director's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now suddenly,\Nshe's just an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a big shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Detective Visbaugh\NOf the Nordhein-Westfalen Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This was such a tragic incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Inspector Heinrich Lunge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Inspector Lunge of the BKA.\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors that\Nyou are a brilliant physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I've still got\Na long ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Have you any idea\Nwhere the children are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have determined what caused
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the death of the director\Nand the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a nitrate type poison\Nin their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitrates...\NThat means a muscular relaxant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a doctor.\NYou are knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The same candy wrapper\Nwas found beside each body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same candy was found\Nin their stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have any idea\Nwhere the three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,might get a hold of\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.\NWhat about the search for the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA has\Ntaken over the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident may have started
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,when the parents of those twins\Nwere shot and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents defected\Nfrom East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and were killed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the director and doctors\Nof the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where the children were taken to\Nwere killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the possibility\Nthat this is political terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children might be\Nholding a major clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the incident, the Director\Nremoved him from his position as Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the Director's daughter\Nbroke off her engagement to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was in a bar drinking\Nat the time of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...\NMay I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you move\Nyour hand like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NOh, I'm typing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inputting all the information into\Nthe disk in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I press the key\Nto extract the information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not at all. I still have\Na long ways to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Dr. Tenma bashfully said\Nwhen I called him brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The police...? Do they suspect you\Nof doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because there's enough evidence\Nfor me to be a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite persistent\Nwhen they questioned me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dust from this thing settles,\NI think I'll go back to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N-I came to Germany to do research,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but due to the recent chain of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've gone back to saving lives,\Nthe true duty of a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your progress is favorable,\NMr. Buchner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Tenma.\NDo you think I can work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My store will go under\Nif I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go have a drink there\Nafter you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to make sure\Nyou don't overdo things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were\Nleaving this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any\Ngood doctors like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say you're quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buchner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, the Chairman\Nis asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The board is discussing who should\Nsucceed to the empty posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, the Director's faction\Nhas filled the major positions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a considerable\Npurging of personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumor is Dr. Eckner\Nis being transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to a small hospital in Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...\N-Umm, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N-No matter what the Chairman says,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.\NI am performance orientated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you are appointed to\NChief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a life...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went against the orders\Nof the Director,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lost my position as Chief,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my engagement to Eva\Nwas dissolved.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As soon as I decide to work\Nas a simple doctor{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without any hope of promotion...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been appointed\NChief of Surgery. That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo... At my father's funeral,\Nyou tried to comfort me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened between us,\Nbut I'd like to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I was wrong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}9 years later\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient hospitalized\Nfor a spinal cord tumor...\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His paralysis has accelerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NI'll perform the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will, Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the arrangements\Nfor the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, when will this flood recede...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the world would change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Berlin Wall came down\Nsix years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing good has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the unification of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless people from all over\Ncome flowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's been an increase in\Nunexplainable crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Both victims had their throats\Nslit open with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reichmanns of Stich Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They were murdered in their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that they were\Nhidden in a closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and their bodies floated out\Nbecause of the flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A murder of a middle-aged couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been four incidents\Nin Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,over the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All by the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a robber who targets\Nrich middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too soon\Nto call them robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the data,\Nfor some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not all of the couples\Nhad children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This couple certainly\Ndidn't have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think there are\Ntoo many similarities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to call them robberies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But money and goods have been\Ntaken from all of the victims' homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them totaling very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make sense\Nif a single perpetrator did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that\Nthere wasn't a single perpetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of the homes had\Nextremely strong locks and alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But the perpetrator opened them\Nand entered very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, none of the couples seemed to \Nfight back when they were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the neighbors didn't hear\Nany noise at the time of the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they were\Ntoo skillfully done
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to have been done by\Na single individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolph Junkers, 32 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been convicted twice\Nfor larceny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His role was to open locks...\NIn other words, he's a lock picker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was seen near the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of three of the murders\Nof middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did this man do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,well...I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the extent\Nof your work as state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't fly after all.\NI've never flown a kite before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how was the girl last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How was she?\NShe was a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, she's the daughter\Nof a director, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you just had dinner\Nand saw her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was an emergency call\Nduring dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to come back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! You'd better rethink that\Nall work and no play doctrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose a great catch\Nand regret it some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening,\NChief of Surgery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A kite...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that yours, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa gave it to me,\Nbut it just won't fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be it's unbalanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can you fly a kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it often during my childhood in\NJapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Try holding it up high, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NNow...will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!\N-There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in his shoes,\NI'd have at least five lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well quickly\Nand fly it yourself, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's surgery is\Na parasellar meningioma extirpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed with\Na right pterional approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. Chief Tenma\Nwill perform the surgery himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a splendid operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hardly retracted the brain at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly is a surgical genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You residents should treat the brain\Nwith tender care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the blood!\N-Ambulance! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't do it!\NIt's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He just ran into the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say...\NThere's nothing more we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a material witness\Nin a certain case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His testimony alone\Ncould solve a serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the patient is\Nin a very critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more can be done\Nat our hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a terrific brain surgeon\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If he came...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way,\NDr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the patient's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in a coma.\NAnd one of his pupils is dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...I'm sorry,\Nbut who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been nine years.\NNot since the Director's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken,\Nyou're with the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make this operation a success\Nfor the sake of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient has to live.\NHe holds the key to solving a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't operate\Nfor the sake of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it for the sake of the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have an operation to perform...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've become\Nthe Chief of Surgery, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been very successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No. At your age,\Nit's quite an accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in line\Nto become the next Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would be\Na long way off for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,About the murders\Nat the Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is very little evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation\Nhas been extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only clue is the poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The methodology means\Nit is an intelligent crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An intelligent crime means
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim and the assailant\Nhave some sort of interests at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, excuse me. In this business,\NI'm constantly thinking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All the cases I've ever handled\Nhave been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will perform a craniotomy\Nto remove the hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hurry. There is the danger\Nof the brain hernia worsening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,only one person greatly benefited from\Nthe Eisler Memorial Hospital murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the trouble\Nto come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. How has\Nthe patient been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's conscious,\Nbut his right pupil remains dilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has some paralysis\Non the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's started rehab already, hasn't he?\NThe paralysis should go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's recovering normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the police will want to see him,\Nbut please refuse for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that detective, Lunge,\Nis so persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the patient's recovery\Nis most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Can you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mons... comi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monster... coming...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming...? What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster is coming...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"For the Love of Life"\NDavid Sylvian - Kuniaki Haishima\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,\N{\fad(1000,0)}\N"The Night of Execution"\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
